      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG BOY BEN (1) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (20.43) at this track in a Maiden over 366m. Capable of going well again. HELLO GEMINI (2) comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 366m behind Anti Venom (20.75) in a Maiden. Was in the money prior to that. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Key runner on best form. MANGO BEACH (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Fins Up Wendy (20.47) in a Maiden. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Hard to beat again. VELVET DASH (5) will have admirers after placing last time out.",
